name: 卡塔琳娜·马汉
name_full: 卡塔琳娜·马汉 Katarina Mahan

last_movies.title: 红鹰战士：天空的守护者

introduction: Katarina Mahan (birth name Patrick Mahan) was born in Santa Rosa, California, USA. Based in the Dallas/Fort Worth, Texas area; She is a trans-female actress, known for her work in horror short films such as Nail Gun (2021) and Alone (2022). Also working as a voice actress for ITN Productions at Spayse Studios.
